# Card Style

Every DaisyUI **card** must have a **primary-colored border**.

Global default in [`src/routes/layout.css`](src/routes/layout.css):

```css
.card {
	@apply border border-primary;
}
```

When adding a card in markup, still use the standard stack:

```svelte
<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-sm">
	<div class="card-body">...</div>
</div>
```

Do **not** remove `border-primary` or override with `border-base-300` unless the element is not a content card (e.g. tables use `rounded-box border border-base-300`, not `.card`).

